{
  "stem": "734.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because our apartment was already taken over by a cook from a hotel, from the Hotel Rome, which was confiscated for the Nazis, became a Nazi club.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And of course, this cook ca-- came in one day with a Nazi officer.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were still living in that, in the apartment.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he said to him that this is the place that he likes to live in.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they told-- well, he didn't have to say much.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, we got the message.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And of course, I mean, once we move out-- excuse me-- we move into the ghetto, you can't do anything.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Anybody can take-- come, come, come in and take it, right?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had no way of dealing with it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so the, this woman and her two daughters moved into my aunt's apartment, and aunt, Grandmother Gotfryd, and us, we got-- we moved into that little house.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was tight, but we managed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And luckily, we had a nice yard, a garden.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was a vegetable garden.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we kept it going for-- we were trying to grow vegetables, except we never-- before the vegetables matured, people would steal them middle of the night.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, there was never anything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We kept on working very hard at it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But we never got anything out of it, really, because hunger in the ghetto was just tremendous.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And anyway, we stayed there till '42, '40-- August '42, till the deportation.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The police on the overall were-- the police consisted of young-- mainly young people, late teens, early 20s, the cream of the crop.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I would say, on the overall, there were some decent boys, except there were some black sheep, too, which we had, we had them, too.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were some nasty characters, some.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
